In":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":104501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-36"}],"nameRight":"露","textRight":"那些内容是真的吗！？@真是不敢置信…","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104501,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-37"}],"nameRight":"露","textRight":"父亲可是被夺走了水名的土地，@为此操尽了心思"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":832100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-38"}],"nameLeft":"露的父亲","textLeft":"别乱说话，露"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":832100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-39"}],"nameLeft":"露的父亲","textLeft":"我原本就从未信任过@野蛮的东边人"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104501,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-40"}],"nameRight":"露","textRight":"那么，您从最开始@就是打算利用千鹤她们…"},{"chara":[{"id":832100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-41"}],"nameLeft":"露的父亲","textLeft":"那是群只要面前有钱袋吊着@就会扑过来抢走的家伙"},{"chara":[{"id":832100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-42"}],"nameLeft":"露的父亲","textLeft":"再没有比他们@更容易成为战力的人了吧"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-43"}],"nameRight":"露","textRight":"我们和他们是一样的！"},{"chara":[{"id":104501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-44"}],"nameRight":"露","textRight":"水名是为了夺回水名的土地，@为了生活于此的人民而战的"},{"chara":[{"id":104501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-45"}],"nameRight":"露","textRight":"他们也想守护好祖辈的土地@挺胸抬头地生活下去"},{"chara":[{"id":832100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-46"}],"nameLeft":"露的父亲","textLeft":"所以，这次我才约定@要将故乡作为封地赐予他们"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104501,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103203/vo_full_103203-7-47"}],"nameRight":"露","textRight":"但是，在那之前@东边的各位都必须暂